  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he was doing that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was sleeping there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And later on, somehow it was saw that I asked this sweeping lady that maybe she has a-- a corner in his-- in her [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so-called apartment.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She lived in some room in this-- in this house, that she could accommodate this-- this boy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she agreed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Of course, the boy was telling her that he will pay for-- for this [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] place to sleep in-- in the corner of her room.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I know that she-- that he-- he was-- he was sleeping there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "When I left Warsaw later on, and I came back, and I asked this lady what happened to this boy, and she said, that oh, he got a job at the airport in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I don't know what happened to him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He didn't show up anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Say again.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that was my present-- present-- my wife.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She asked me to help her to escape from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because, you see, because of the situation and lack of-- of sympathy, a lack of, yeah, I would say the sympathy.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Understanding what's going on and suffering of Jews, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] my present wife, she felt that she's not secure, not safe, staying, living in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she approached me to-- to help her to find a place or connections.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see in Warsaw, everything was based on connection, on if you knew somebody and so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sometimes you have to bribe this person or to give some money that some other person has to be bribed from it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we-- that was every day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] acquaintance with my wife went to that precedence, or-- or that-- that she wanted to go away from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
